==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blue Hen State
<hw>Blue Hen State</hw>. <def>The State of Delaware; -- a popular
sobriquet. It is said, though the story lacks proof, to have taken its
origin from the insistence of a Delaware Revolutionary captain, named
Caldwell, that no cock could be truly game unless the mother was a blue
hen, whence <col><b>Blue Hen's Chickens</b></col> came to be a nickname
for the people of Delaware.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

